{"title":"大山","authors":["李奇生"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":12,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李奇生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一座大山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍巍耸立在云端。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历经时代沧桑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目睹风云变幻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂风刮去的是败叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷霆抖落的是朽岩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴雨冲洗着尘埃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈日蒸腾着雾幔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一座大山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不改初衷的热恋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鄙夷海市蜃楼的奇观，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不羡落日晚霞的妖艳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小草染绿我的躯干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清泉注入我的血管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大鹏在我头上盘旋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪莲在我胸前初绽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一座大山哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永属于生机盎然。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使有涅槃的一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那也是我奔向母亲的新起点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：吉林化学工业公司）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}